  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pocket Rogues</strong> is a dynamic, old-school <strong>Action-RPG</strong> with <strong>Roguelike</strong> elements. Here, you’ll fight your way through hordes of monsters, explore unique, randomly generated locations, and develop your own fortress and heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=544 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Pocket Rogues</strong>, you’ll discover dozens of dungeons filled with unique loot and monsters, a variety of hero classes, and terrifying bosses—each encounter presenting a true challenge. <strong>Traditional RPG elements, such as character progression and exploration, ensure you’ll never get bored!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=538 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"For centuries, this dark dungeon has lured hapless travelers with its secrets and treasures. One by one, they vanished, consumed by true Evil. Yet grim legends only fuel the desires of ever more adventurers. Why not become one of them?!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Completely real-time gameplay</u>!</strong> Move, dodge, and flank your enemies! The combat system emphasizes precise character control and player skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Multiple hero classes</u>:</strong> Each class has unique skills, specialized equipment, and its own development tree.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Every descent is unique</u>!</strong> From locations and monsters to loot and random encounters, everything is procedurally generated. No two dungeons are ever the same!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Distinct locations</u>:</strong> Each one features its own visual style, unique enemies, traps, and interactive objects. Move freely between all unlocked locations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Build your own fortress</u>:</strong> Construct and upgrade buildings in your Guild Fortress to unlock and enhance new heroes and gain access to new game mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Regular updates</u>:</strong> The game has been actively supported and developed over time, with constant input from the community and dedicated players.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pocket Rogues</strong> is a dynamic, old-school <strong>Action-RPG</strong> with <strong>Roguelike</strong> elements. Here, you’ll fight your way through hordes of monsters, explore unique, randomly generated locations, and develop your own fortress and heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=544 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/68db6ba23a297b3e74ff3c38b3e5ccd8.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Pocket Rogues</strong>, you’ll discover dozens of dungeons filled with unique loot and monsters, a variety of hero classes, and terrifying bosses—each encounter presenting a true challenge. <strong>Traditional RPG elements, such as character progression and exploration, ensure you’ll never get bored!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=538 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/fcfd80142b74f268571b3401f1a85e19.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"For centuries, this dark dungeon has lured hapless travelers with its secrets and treasures. One by one, they vanished, consumed by true Evil. Yet grim legends only fuel the desires of ever more adventurers. Why not become one of them?!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.poster.avif?t=1756992179\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.webm?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/946610/extras/e45625c8d41c69e1814f337099cd110d.mp4?t=1756992179\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Completely real-time gameplay</u>!</strong> Move, dodge, and flank your enemies! The combat system emphasizes precise character control and player skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Multiple hero classes</u>:</strong> Each class has unique skills, specialized equipment, and its own development tree.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Every descent is unique</u>!</strong> From locations and monsters to loot and random encounters, everything is procedurally generated. No two dungeons are ever the same!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Distinct locations</u>:</strong> Each one features its own visual style, unique enemies, traps, and interactive objects. Move freely between all unlocked locations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Build your own fortress</u>:</strong> Construct and upgrade buildings in your Guild Fortress to unlock and enhance new heroes and gain access to new game mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Regular updates</u>:</strong> The game has been actively supported and developed over time, with constant input from the community and dedicated players.</p></li></ul>",
